{"type": "article", "id": 22745, "title": "MSDS 极简家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-24T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122214Rs4EYPngrvkuipZf.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是加拿大设计事务所 MSDS 带来的家具系列，也是一组北欧式的极简家具。椅子借用了 17 世纪温莎椅的风格，椅腿和靠背微微倾斜，但三根腿的结构让这把椅子更加简洁。边桌用木材、铝和石材三种材料设计一种相似的造型，都从横梁上延伸出新的支撑，却有不同的表达方式，很有趣。陶制的桌灯像微微打开的花瓣，带来略有渐变的温和光影。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060712221175UdnADPCXfczNT4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122212Wek1lGrya36POV4j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64102564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122212BTu7q2jw6Yz53nH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122212W1axRKCPwiIpA7Ms.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122213gA1ZCuKiVtn5H6Wh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}